    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  acute (&lt;6 weeks) back pain

          -  &gt;20 und &lt;60 years of age

          -  good oral and written knowledge of German language

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  any treatment for back pain within the last 6 months

          -  Cauda equina

          -  tumor

          -  generalized pain

          -  severe systemic illness

          -  substance abuse

          -  pregnancy
      </textblock>
